There Are two (2) methodologies for completeley unenrolling your chromos device at boot, The first is sh1mmer, well documented and patched by google.
The second is the "pencil method" poorly documented and with hardware modifications required. This method is not very well documented and I have only ever
seen it as a kajig on the 
titanium network discord server (https://discord.gg/unblock)
The second is called the "Kethup Kajig" and is housed at (https://rentry.co/5yk7thr) This one is self explanitory although quetionably trolly.
